docs.snippet: I agree with everything Admiral Phelps wrote condemning mandatory embargo provisions in neutrality laws except that we entered the last war in order to change the form of the German Government. This argument was used by President Wilson to disaffect...
docs.lead_paragraph: I agree with everything Admiral Phelps wrote condemning mandatory embargo provisions in neutrality laws except that we entered the last war in order to change the form of the German Government. This argument was used by President Wilson to disaffect German morale; certainly a worthy propaganda instrument of war.
